version_description: Neat accurate formatting, chord legend and additional tabbed info on main riff.

I have simplified the song by taking out some of the F#m7's and putting Dmaj7' in their place. It makes the song super easy to play. If you want to add them back in, they are in the Chorus and can be substituted back in.
Complete and thoroughly ear-transcribed chords / intermediate with split chords and suggestins for playable voicings / short tab for basic pattern / link to demo recording.
